### CREATE TASK (Admin only - login as admin first, set assignee to a user's _id)
POST http://localhost:5000/task-api/tasks
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "title": "Build backend",
  "description": "Complete task manager APIs",
  "status": "PENDING",
  "priority": "HIGH",
  "dueDate": "2026-05-30",
  "assignee": "USER_ID_HERE"
}

### GET ALL TASKS (Admin: all tasks, User: only assigned tasks)
GET http://localhost:5000/task-api/tasks


### GET SINGLE TASK
GET http://localhost:5000/task-api/tasks/TASK_ID_HERE


### UPDATE TASK (Admin: all fields, User: status only)
PUT http://localhost:5000/task-api/tasks/TASK_ID_HERE
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "status": "IN_PROGRESS"
}


### UPDATE FULL TASK (Admin only)
PUT http://localhost:5000/task-api/tasks/TASK_ID_HERE
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "title": "Complete MERN Task App",
  "description": "Backend + Frontend + Deployment",
  "status": "COMPLETED",
  "priority": "HIGH",
  "dueDate": "2026-06-10"
}


### DELETE TASK (Admin only)
DELETE http://localhost:5000/task-api/tasks/TASK_ID_HERE